  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/21319e543a1a5c1fe17172f514c9ab03.avif?t=1744459461\" width=614 height=1178 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/e492ab1689c0229b20cd36f38c57fbfd.avif?t=1744459461\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><strong>TINY ATOLLS</strong> is a minimalist building strategy game<br>Expand across colorful islands, unlock new tiles and complete quests!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/53542a54973cc76995168576645b8d39.poster.avif?t=1744459461\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/53542a54973cc76995168576645b8d39.webm?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/53542a54973cc76995168576645b8d39.mp4?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/c6861252640de860d78b2146647a0db3.avif?t=1744459461\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><strong>TINY ATOLLS</strong> centers around the art of forging meaningful connections between different types and colors. The higher the number of connections you establish, the greater your score and the more tiles you can strategically position.<br><br>Beyond standard tiles, an assortment of card tools becomes at your disposal, offering the means to expand your diminutive settlements. As you unravel quests and amass points, you unlock the ability to select the precise tools required for venturing to new islands and reshaping the picturesque landscapes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/19bc65a674c34a0a3a931e44bc3932a7.poster.avif?t=1744459461\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/19bc65a674c34a0a3a931e44bc3932a7.webm?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/19bc65a674c34a0a3a931e44bc3932a7.mp4?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Some quests are special and will ask for specific tiles to be placed in order to build unique buildings with various new mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/c04483fb23828843413ea3c00c7cd13f.poster.avif?t=1744459461\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/c04483fb23828843413ea3c00c7cd13f.webm?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/c04483fb23828843413ea3c00c7cd13f.mp4?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/684734fec2624d9fe1c7ebbb49b78294.avif?t=1744459461\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedurally generated islands<br></li><li>Quests and unlockable tiles<br></li><li>Beautiful, vibrant colors<br></li><li>Modular tiling<br></li><li>Calm and cozy atmosphere<br></li><li>Online leaderboard</li></ul>",
